<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Happy Birthday Sweetheart</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #ff9a9e, #fad0c4);
      color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .countdown, .message {
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    }
    .countdown {
      font-size: 5em;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .message {
      display: none;
      font-size: 2em;
      line-height: 1.5;
      max-width: 700px;
    }
    .kiss {
      font-size: 3em;
      margin-top: 20px;
      animation: kiss 1s infinite alternate;
    }
    @keyframes kiss {
      from { transform: scale(1); }
      to { transform: scale(1.2); }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="countdown" id="countdown">3</div>
  <div class="message" id="message">
    <h1>🎉 Happy Birthday Sweetheart 🎉</h1>
    <p>
      Today is all about celebrating you—the most amazing person in my life.  
      These past 6 months together have been the happiest of my life, and I’m so grateful for every smile, every laugh, and every moment we’ve shared.  
      You make my world brighter, and I can’t wait for all the adventures ahead with you.  
    </p>
    <p class="kiss">💋 Sending you a big kiss 💋</p>
  </div>

  <script>
    let countdown = document.getElementById('countdown');
    let message = document.getElementById('message');
    let numbers = ["3", "2", "1", "Go!"];
    let i = 0;

    function showCountdown() {
      if (i < numbers.length) {
        countdown.textContent = numbers[i];
        i++;
        setTimeout(showCountdown, 1000);
      } else {
        countdown.style.display = "none";
        message.style.display = "block";
      }
    }

    showCountdown();
  </script>
</body>
</html>
